00:08.609 --> 00:13.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, President of the
United States:
General H.R. McMaster will
become the national

00:13.447 --> 00:15.415 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
