resort in Florida.

01:21.014 --> 01:24.618 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, President of the
United States:
He's a man of tremendous talent
and tremendous

01:24.651 --> 01:25.619 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
experience.

01:25.652 --> 01:29.756 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
