to have him.

01:35.929 --> 01:38.098 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
H.R. MCMASTER, U.S. National
Security Adviser:
I would just like to say what a
privilege

01:38.131 --> 01:40.634 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
