opportunity,
and I look forward to joining
the national

01:44.538 --> 01:49.276 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
security team and doing
everything I can to
advance and protect the interest
of the American

01:49.309 --> 01:50.277 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
people.

01:50.310 --> 01:51.278 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Thank you very much.

01:51.311 --> 01:53.013 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: You're going to do
a great job.

01:53.046 --> 01:57.084 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: For some
background on H.R.
McMaster: He's 54 years old and
currently

01:57.117 --> 01:59.886 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
a three-star general in the U.S.
Army.

01:59.920 --> 02:06.159 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
