and the violence,
and then focused on rebuilding.

04:18.992 --> 04:21.695 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, it became a strategy known
as clear, hold
and build.

04:21.728 --> 04:23.263 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Clear, hold and
build.

04:23.296 --> 04:27.134 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
How is he viewed, Greg Jaffe, by
the rest
of the Army, by the military?

04:27.167 --> 04:32.806 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GREG JAFFE: I think, in many
cases, with great
admiration, because he's so
frank, he's so

04:32.839 --> 04:33.807 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
smart.

04:33.840 --> 04:35.709 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It's interesting, though.

04:35.742 --> 04:40.480 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When he was promoted from
colonel to one-star,
he was passed for promotion to
one-star general

04:40.514 --> 04:41.915 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
twice.

04:41.948 --> 04:45.485 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think in some cases, that
was a reflection
on how frank he can be.

04:45.519 --> 04:49.756 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
He doesn't hold back his
opinions and sometimes
that rubs folks the wrong way.

04:49.789 --> 04:53.426 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Is there a
political philosophy
there, or are you talking about
a philosophy

04:53.460 --> 04:55.262 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of war, of fighting?

04:55.295 --> 04:58.465 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GREG JAFFE: A philosophy of war
and fighting.

04:58.498 --> 05:01.601 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He's not a political guy in any
way, shape
or form.

05:01.635 --> 05:03.470 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I think that is interesting,
too.

05:03.503 --> 05:08.708 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I don't think he will bring --
he won't bring
very sharp political instincts
on the downside.

05:08.742 --> 05:11.211 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
On the upside, he's not a
political ideologue.

05:11.244 --> 05:13.280 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He has very strong opinions
about war, though.

05:13.313 --> 05:16.183 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You were telling
me -- we were
talking about how he's a -- you
said he's

05:16.216 --> 05:17.951 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
a prolific writer.

05:17.984 --> 05:22.689 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He's written a lot for -- we
were looking
at the Web site for the Hoover
Institution,

05:22.722 --> 05:24.891 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
