middle of power
at the White House?

05:50.850 --> 05:52.719 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GREG JAFFE: Yes, I think that
will be interesting.

05:52.752 --> 05:57.924 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He has dealt a lot in Tal Afar
and then in
Iraq he ran -- or -- I'm sorry
-- in Afghanistan,

05:57.958 --> 06:01.728 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
