force for General
Petraeus in 2010.

06:01.761 --> 06:04.698 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so that meant he had to deal
with a lot
of arms of government.

06:04.731 --> 06:06.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He had to deal with the State
Department.

06:06.600 --> 06:10.036 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
He had to deal with the
intelligence agencies,
all those things that you have
to deal with

06:10.070 --> 06:11.805 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
