worrying about politics in
Washington.

06:15.542 --> 06:19.312 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think that's going to be a
challenge
and a stretch for him, because
the national

06:19.346 --> 06:23.850 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
