a retired general at the
Pentagon.

06:33.159 --> 06:36.863 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We're seeing a lot of military
people in this
administration.

06:36.896 --> 06:37.864 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GREG JAFFE: Yes, that's right.

06:37.897 --> 06:40.000 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And it will be interesting.

06:40.033 --> 06:41.701 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's an interesting dynamic,
