choice.

06:49.309 --> 06:52.245 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it sounds like he's somebody
very different
from Michael Flynn.

06:52.279 --> 06:54.047 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GREG JAFFE: Yes, I think he is.

06:54.080 --> 06:57.884 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
