figure than
Flynn would be, much less of an
erratic figure.

07:02.656 --> 07:05.792 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Greg Jaffe with
The Washington
Post, thank you so much.

07:05.825 --> 07:06.793 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
GREG JAFFE: Sure.

07:06.826 --> 07:08.561 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
