33:50.762 --> 33:51.997 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That's the challenge.

33:52.030 --> 33:54.499 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, what we're seeing is two
sides really,
really fired up.

33:54.532 --> 33:56.268 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
