34:03.642 --> 34:04.542 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The geography
problem, you
have written about this.

34:04.576 --> 34:05.877 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
AMY WALTER: Yes.

34:05.911 --> 34:10.615 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
