48:12.089 --> 48:17.161 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TARELL ALVIN MCCRANEY: It often
pains me to
know that people sort of see
him, and go,

48:17.194 --> 48:18.929 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
oh, that's unusual.

48:18.963 --> 48:22.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When I think -- when I think
back over my
