49:11.982 --> 49:15.319 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think the voice of this
character is one
in particular that people
haven't heard very

49:15.352 --> 49:16.320 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
often.

49:16.353 --> 49:18.122 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And they're curious.

49:18.155 --> 49:20.357 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
