similar to

49:20.391 --> 49:22.193 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
mine.

49:22.226 --> 49:24.728 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I kind of relate to this guy,
even though
I don't want to sit next to him
on the subway.

49:24.762 --> 49:26.564 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Maybe I will next time.

49:26.597 --> 49:30.534 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TARELL ALVIN MCCRANEY: And now I
