50:57.721 --> 50:59.623 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It's incredible how big they are
and lifelike.

50:59.657 --> 51:04.728 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JULIA GRIFFIN: The statues are
big, but attendance
was low, and the venture went
belly up in

51:04.762 --> 51:06.563 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
2010.

51:06.597 --> 51:10.701 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When the Presidents Park was
forced to close,
the presidential busts were
destined for a

51:10.734 --> 51:12.469 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
