51:12.503 --> 51:17.174 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Rather than let that happen,
Hankins decide
to bring them here, to his
family farm in

51:17.207 --> 51:18.976 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Virginia.

51:19.009 --> 51:24.448 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
