51:26.717 --> 51:30.688 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HOWARD HANKINS: I got a ladder,
climbed up
on top, popped a hole in their
head, and rocked

51:30.721 --> 51:35.492 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
