about a 70,000-pound
machine, and picked them up and
put them on

51:35.526 --> 51:37.127 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
my lowboys and brought them
here.

51:37.161 --> 51:40.030 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JULIA GRIFFIN: Abraham Lincoln,
in particular,
took a beating.

51:40.064 --> 51:43.767 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HOWARD HANKINS: Lincoln over
there, we dropped
him on his -- back of his head.

51:43.801 --> 51:47.137 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
