the chain
broke, and we dropped him.

51:47.171 --> 51:49.406 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JULIA GRIFFIN: The busts can be
repaired.

51:49.440 --> 51:52.609 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
