elements take
their toll.

51:52.643 --> 51:56.647 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HOWARD HANKINS: Being out of
concrete, the
water gets in and freezes and
cracks them.

51:56.680 --> 52:02.886 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They kind of have character the
way they are,
I mean, a little mold and moss
on them and

52:02.920 --> 52:04.755 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
